    <p><strong>Skip this if...</strong> you need low-noise grinding or bigger family-size output.</p>
    <ProsCons
      pros={["Simple controls that are easy half-awake.", "Handles beans, grounds, and K-Cup styles.", "Reliable weekday pace for solo drinkers."]}
      cons={["Blade grinding can flatten cup clarity.", "Needs regular descale cadence to keep flow stable."]}
    />
